{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3fdd13b73a","title":"对一个工人关于物价上涨的来信的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7b8570d164","index":0,"year":1962,"month":3,"day":4,"articleId":"3fdd13b73a"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji45","name":"毛泽东全集第45卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/45-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji45":{"comments":[{"id":"509269ff37","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"3fdd13b73a","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在中共中央办公厅秘书室1962年2月23日编印的《群众反映》第十三期上。这一期登载了上海市工人金祥根1962年2月12日给毛泽东的信，信中说，最近物价不断提高，真使人坐卧不宁。我们工人响应党的号召，节衣缩食，10多年来积蓄的一些钱，眼看着一天天地账值，心里比刀割还难过，现在有很多人看到这种情况，不想再储蓄了。为此，我提出两项建议：（一）政府尽最大努力稳住物价，使人民对币值有充分的信心。（二）每月公布物价总指数，存款采取保本保值的办法。"},{"id":"ef4b6731f4","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"3fdd13b73a","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"先念，即李先念，当时任中共中央书记处书记、中央财经小组副组长、国务院副总理。"}],"contents":[{"id":"b06a2ff47f","type":"title","text":"对一个工人关于物价上涨的来信的批语则","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"3fdd13b73a"},{"id":"509269ff37","type":"paragraph","text":"先念时同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"3fdd13b73a"},{"id":"ef4b6731f4","type":"paragraph","text":"请你找几个内行同志在一起，研究一下，看这个文内所提两项办法是否可能做到，怎样做到，何时做到。如有结果，请告我","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"3fdd13b73a"},{"id":"806f7aa495","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"3fdd13b73a"},{"id":"c7a5b75ebd","type":"paragraph","text":"三月四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"3fdd13b73a"}],"page":{"id":"af172c5cbe","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"3fdd13b73a","start":95,"end":95}}}},"__N_SSG":true}